title: Women of iHeartCountry with Amy Brown + Guest: Ashley McBryde Her Horseback Riding Accident, Bathing Cats Debate and Performance
itunes:title: Women of iHeartCountry with Amy Brown + Guest: Ashley McBryde Her Horseback Riding Accident, Bathing Cats Debate and Performance
description:
Amy does a show every weekend called Women of iHeartCountry and her latest guest included Ashley McBryde! Check out the full interview with Amy and Ashley talked about her horse riding accident, helps settle a debate on bathing cats and shared the story behind her new duet with Carly Pearce “Never Wanted to Be That Girl”.  Plus Ashley performs! 

You can listen to Women of iHeartCountry, hosted by Amy, every weekend! Just check out your local iHeartRadio station or search Women of iHeartCountry on your iHeartRadio App. And be sure to follow on Instagram @WomeniHeartCountry

 

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
